channel.title: Load Error Starting Up 20
channel.description:
Hi,
I've Jar'd my client using jar maker. I have also got my cache set, the downloading works but the client would not start.
If i open it with the debuger that the jar maker produces for me via the client.bat i get this error.
[code]C:\Users\*****\Desktop>java -jar client.jar File could not be found. Error: loaderror Starting up 20[/code]#
Can I please get help with this? Signing it and Making the webclient also works using jar maker but I believe there is something wrong with the client itself, the files.
This is a 317 delta.
